title: Daughters of the Sexual Revolution: The Untold Story of the Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders

sources.title: The Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders | Comedy Drama | Jane Seymour | Lauren Tewes
sources.description:
**This film is under license from Vision Films Inc. All rights reserved**

The Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders - A newspaper editor decides to send his girlfriend, who is also a reporter on the paper, undercover to try out for the cheerleading team for the Dallas Cowboys in order to do an "insider's" story.  Stars Jane Seymour

1979
Stars: Jane Seymour, Laraine Stephens, Bert Convy

metadata.Plot: The never-before-told story of Suzanne Mitchell, the fiercely-loyal den mother of the original Dallas Cowboys Cheerleaders. Seen by many as regressive and exploitative, this diverse sisterhood of small-town "girls next door" became a controversial pop culture phenomenon at the height of the Sexual Revolution, changing the game of football -- and America -- forever.
metadata.Actors: Cindy Bennett, Muhammad Ali, Vonciel Baker
